description: This file defines the API for the Beep Environment Request Object, including function prototypes for creation, removal, object enrollment, and initialization within the BSP execution environment. It serves as an interface for other components to interact with the Beep Env Request Object.

methods.name: BeepCreateEnvRequest
methods.description: Creates a new Beep Environment Request Object with context handles.

methods.name: BeepEnvReqoCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Beep Env Request Object.

methods.name: BeepEnvReqoRemove
methods.description: Removes the Beep Env Request Object instance.

methods.name: BeepEnvReqoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects for the Beep Env Request Object.

methods.name: BeepEnvReqoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Beep Env Request Object.
